  "text": "The prior P (θ|M ) for the parameters is assumed to be the Dirichlet distribution that is a conjugate prior distribution for the multinomial. This assumption, together with certain additional technical assumptions (see e.g. [CITATION_1] ), allows us to compute the marginal likelihood term in Eq. (3) in closed form:",
